      "title": "Schools in Colombo and other major cities to remain closed next week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education says that schools in the Colombo Zone and other major cities will remain closed next week, from June 27 to July 01.",
        "However, the ministry said that rural schools can function as normal on Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday during the week."
      ],
